*Oružje* je izuzetno opasno (Weapons are extremely dangerous).

Nadležni organi su uhapsili krivičnu grupu koja se bavila krijumčarenjem *oružja* (The authorities arrested a criminal group involved in smuggling of weapons).

Sankcije su izrečene za nelegalno posedovanje *oružja* (Sanctions were imposed for illegal possession of weapons).

Od kada je zabranjeno korišćenje *oružja*, naselje je postalo mirnije (Since the use of weapons has been prohibited, the settlement has become calmer).

Nemačka vlada je naredila da se sva *oružja* skloni iz zemlje (The German government ordered all weapons to be removed from the country).